  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the trial is to assess Adrenal Suppression potential when pediatric subjects are
      administered Product 0405 for the treatment of Atopic Dermatitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Treatment medication will be administered topically, twice a day for 4 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
